properties.name: Saint Walstan's Memorial And Wayside Chapel
properties.note: Here lies a triangular memorial to the Anglo Saxon Saint, Walstan. It is set beside a wayside chapel and follows the Saxon rules of design. The wayside chapel is a place of prayer and reflection.
